"title": "4915: completion",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4915",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The bringing to fulfilment of a work, such as the work of creation or redemption.</p>\n<h2>Creation was completed by the seventh day</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:1-Gen2:2\">GEN 2:1–2:2</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:4\">DEU 32:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:3-Gen1:4\">GEN 1:3–1:4</a> <em>Genesis chapter 1 records the creation completed on each successive day as being “good”</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:11\">EXO 20:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:3\">JHN 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:16\">COL 1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:2\">HEB 1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:3\">HEB 4:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:3\">HEB 11:3</a></p>\n<h2>All things are completed in God's time</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:4\">GAL 4:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:16\">GEN 15:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:24\">DAN 9:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:15\">MRK 1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:6\">ROM 5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:10\">EPH 1:10</a></p>\n<h2>The work of redemption is a completed work</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ brought his earthly work to completion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:4\">JHN 17:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:30\">JHN 19:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:34\">JHN 4:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:36\">JHN 5:36</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ will present his church complete to his Father</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:37-John6:40\">JHN 6:37–6:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:45\">JHN 6:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:24\">JHN 17:24</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ makes his people complete in himself</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:19\">EPH 3:19</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:6\">PHP 1:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:10\">COL 2:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:11\">JHN 15:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:24\">JHN 16:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:14\">ROM 15:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:2\">COL 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:4\">JAS 1:4</a></p>\n<h2>Believers are to complete their God- given work</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:24\">ACT 20:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:26\">ACT 14:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:28\">ROM 15:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:17\">COL 4:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:7\">2TI 4:7</a></p>\n<h2>The completion of the age</h2>\n<h3>This world will come to an end</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:17\">ISA 65:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:22\">ISA 66:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:28\">MAT 19:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:9-Eph1:10\">EPH 1:9–1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:11-Heb1:12\">HEB 1:11–1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:10-2Pet3:12\">2PE 3:10–3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:1-Rev21:5\">REV 21:1–21:5</a></p>\n<h3>There will be a final separation of the righteous and wicked</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:36-Matt13:43\">MAT 13:36–13:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:47-Matt13:50\">MAT 13:47–13:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:32-Matt25:41\">MAT 25:32–25:41</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:8-2Thess1:10\">2TH 1:8–1:10</a></p>",
